## How to Build & Launch

1. `npm init`, copy files, `npm i`.
2. `npm run compile`, F5 for dev.
3. Backend: `npx wrangler@3 init bioworld-server`, deploy.
4. Test flow: Login → chat in lab → submit dummy pipeline → see leaderboard update.
5. Publish: VS Marketplace → invite your GitHub followers.
6. Monetize: Stripe in backend for subs; Gumroad for pro tools.

